  "instructions": [
    "Peel the potatoes and cut them into 1-inch cubes. Place the potatoes in a large bowl and drizzle with 2 tablespoons of the olive oil, tossing to coat. Sprinkle the potatoes with the smoked paprika, salt, black pepper, and cayenne pepper, and toss to combine."
